How to install plug-ins?1. Create a folder with a name like "Plug-Ins" 2. Put your plug-ins into that folder3. Launch GraphicConverter4. Choose Preferences from the File menu and click on Plug-Ins under the General options 5. Click on "Select folder"6. Select the folder you created in step 17. Click "Select"8. Click "Ok"9. Quit GraphicConverter10. Start GraphicConverterThe plug-ins are now active.Regards,Lemke Software